= Dragon Warrior (NES) - Values =

This page documents the '''game constants, item IDs, and equipment values''' for Dragon Warrior (NES).

==Overview==

Dragon Warrior stores equipment data in a compact format using bit fields in a single byte. This page documents the various ID values and their meanings.

