==Battle System Constants==

===Damage Formulas===

'''Player Physical Attack:'''
* Base Damage = (Player ATK / 2) - (Enemy DEF / 4)
* Final Damage = Base Damage + Random(0, 4)
* If Final Damage < 0: Final Damage = 0

'''Enemy Physical Attack:'''
* Base Damage = (Enemy STR / 2) - (Player DEF / 4)
* Final Damage = Base Damage + Random(0, 4)
* If Final Damage < 0: Final Damage = 0

'''Critical Hits:'''
* Chance = Player AGI / 64 (out of 256)
* Critical Damage = Normal Damage × 2

===Hit/Miss Formulas===

'''Player Hit Chance:'''
* Base = 224/256 (87.5%)
* Penalty = Enemy AGI / 4
* Final = Base - Penalty

'''Enemy Hit Chance:'''
* Base = 192/256 (75%)
* Penalty = Player AGI / 2
* Final = Base - Penalty

'''Dodge Chance:'''
* Chance = Player AGI / 4 (out of 256)

