* Agility Bonus = (Player AGI - Enemy AGI) / 4
* Final = Base + Bonus
* Minimum = 64/256 (25%)
* Maximum = 224/256 (87.5%)
* Special monsters (Metal Slime, Goldman): Always flee successfully

